mage.Editor
Class GenbankWriter

java.lang.Object
  mage.Editor.GenbankWriter

public class GenbankWriter
extends java.lang.Object

GenbankWriter is a wrapper for creating a genbank file from Merlin Results. The features are intended to be read by MageEditor

Author:
SamirAhmed
